doctype html
html(lang="en")
  head
    meta(charset="UTF-8")
    meta(name="viewport", content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0")
    title Update Appointment, Barangay Santa Monica Services from Quezon City. 
    style.
      body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 20px;
        font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
        background-color: #f1f1f1;
      }
      @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
        body {
          padding: 10px !important;
        }

        div[style*="max-width:600px"] {
          max-width: 100% !important;
          margin: 0 auto !important;
          border-radius: 0 !important;
        }

        div[style*="padding:32px 40px"] {
          padding: 20px !important;
        }

        div[style*="padding:36px"] {
          padding: 24px !important;
        }

        img {
          width: 150px !important;
          height: auto !important;
        }

        div[style*="font-size:24px"] {
          font-size: 20px !important;
        }

        div[style*="font-size:14px"] {
          font-size: 13px !important;
          line-height: 1.5 !important;
        }

        div[style*="padding:16px 40px"] {
          padding: 12px 20px !important;
        }
      }

  body
    div(style="max-width:600px;margin:0 auto;background-color:#ffffff;border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);border: 1px solid #E2E8F0;")
      
      // Header
      div(style="background-color:#227D53;text-align:center;")
        div(style="display:inline-block;")
          img(src="https://95306gu5u4.ufs.sh/f/uBRuoG2BEPFDBrb1g0aDM9AeOZ3oCyXH0dsq5UuJjlR2vx1t", alt="Unofficial Logo", style="width:200px;object-fit:cover;")

      // Content
      div(style="padding:32px 40px;color:#333333;line-height:1.6;")
        div(style="margin-bottom:16px;font-size:24px;font-weight:700;")
          | Greetings,
        
        div(style="margin-bottom:16px;font-size:14px;")
          | Para sa ating update sa iyong telekonsulta appointment someone from the staff 

        div(style="margin-bottom:16px;font-size:14px;")
          | Below are the latest details of your appointment.

        table(width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="border-collapse:collapse;max-width:600px;margin:20px auto;background:#ffffff;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;")
          tr
            th(style="background:#f7f7f7;text-align:left;padding:12px;border-bottom:1px solid #e5e5e5;width:35%;font-size:14px;font-weight:600;")
              | Field
            th(style="background:#f7f7f7;text-align:left;padding:12px;border-bottom:1px solid #e5e5e5;font-size:14px;font-weight:600;")
              | Value

          tr
            td(style="padding:12px;border-bottom:1px solid #f0f0f0;font-size:14px;")
              | Scheduled Date
            td(style="padding:12px;border-bottom:1px solid #f0f0f0;font-size:14px;")
              | #{appointment.date_scheduled_formatted}

          tr
            td(style="padding:12px;border-bottom:1px solid #f0f0f0;font-size:14px;")
              | Category
            td(style="padding:12px;border-bottom:1px solid #f0f0f0;font-size:14px;")
              | #{appointment.category}

          tr
            td(style="padding:12px;border-bottom:1px solid #f0f0f0;font-size:14px;")
              | Details
            td(style="padding:12px;border-bottom:1px solid #f0f0f0;font-size:14px;white-space:pre-line;")
              | #{appointment.details}

          tr
            td(style="padding:12px;font-size:14px;")
              | Status 
            td(style="padding:12px;font-size:14px;white-space:pre-line;")
              | #{appointment.status}

          tr
            td(style="padding:12px;font-size:14px;")
              | Remarks
            td(style="padding:12px;font-size:14px;white-space:pre-line;")
              | #{appointment.remarks}

        div(style="margin-bottom:16px;font-size:14px;")
          | Kung may questions pwede rin mag-chat sa ating platform o dito nalang mismo sa ating email.

        div(style="margin-bottom:16px;font-size:14px;")
          | This service account is open for replies / inquiries. Kung may questions, feel free to respond directly to this message.

        div(style="margin-top:16px;font-size:14px;")
          | Maraming Salamat sa Suporta mula sa ating Barangay.

        div(style="margin-top:16px;font-size:14px;")
          | Lubos na gumagalang,
          br
          | Barangay Santa Monica, Kasama mo sa pag-unlad!

      // Footer
      div(style="background-color:#f4f4f4;padding:16px 40px;font-size:12px;color:#666666;line-height:1.5;text-align:center;")
        p(style="margin:0;")
          | Barangay Santa Monica is one of the progressive barangays located in District 5 & Novaliches, under the administrative jurisdiction of Quezon City Hall. Novaliches District Center, Jordan Plains, Barangay Sta. Monica.
        p(style="margin: 12px 0 0 0;")
          | Â© #{new Date().getFullYear()}, Barangay Santa Monica of Quezon City, All rights reserved.
